ult\" locked=\"off\"]<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><b>Ed</b><br /><span>Web Developer</span></p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" locked=\"off\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_divider color=\"#efefef\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#f2f2f2\" height=\"1px\" custom_margin=\"30px||30px||true|false\" border_color_all=\"#cccccc\" border_width_all_tablet=\"\" border_width_all_phone=\"\" border_width_all_last_edited=\"on|desktop\"][/et_pb_divider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=\"1_2,1_2\" module_class=\"about-column-sec2 vertical-align-middle\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" locked=\"off\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_text module_class=\"about-column-sec2-text\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"]<h2>Google Certified Partner</h2>\nWe are proud to hold the prestigious title of being a Google Partner.\nAchieving Partner status means The HOTH has demonstrated Google Ads skill and expertise, met Google ad spend requirements, delivered company agency and client revenue growth, and sustained and grown its client base.[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_image src=\"https://wp.localserverweb.com/thehoth/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/google-partner-RGB-search-disp-e1588871518542.png\" title_text=\"google-partner-RGB-search-disp-e1588871518542\" align=\"center\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" locked=\"off\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_divider color=\"#efefef\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#f2f2f2\" height=\"1px\" custom_margin=\"30px||30px||true|false\" border_color_all=\"#cccccc\" border_width_all_tablet=\"\" border_width_all_phone=\"\" border_width_all_last_edited=\"on|desktop\"][/et_pb_divider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row module_class=\"faq-sec\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" locked=\"off\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_text module_class=\"faq-sec-title font-size-36 head-light\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"]<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">The History</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">We’ve come a long way.</p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text module_class=\"faq-sec-list\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" max_width=\"760px\" module_alignment=\"center\"]<h3><b>Before The HOTH</b></h3>\n<p>Before the birth of The HOTH, we ran a full-service SEO agency in Chicago that ranked clients for some of the hardest terms online.</p>\n<p>As the agency grew, we saw lots of changes in SEO. We experimented with all different forms of link building, including lots of manual link building. Some things worked, others didn’t. Then<span> </span><a href=\"https://www.thehoth.com/google-update-history/\">Google would change it’s algorithm</a> with<span> </span><a title=\"Google Panda Updates\" href=\"https://www.thehoth.com/google-update-history/panda-algorithm-update-guide/\">Panda</a><span> </span>or<span> </span><a title=\"Google Penguin Updates\" href=\"https://www.thehoth.com/google-update-history/penguin-algorithm-update-guide/\">Penguin</a><span> </span>and everything would need to be restarted from the beginning. Then we invented what is now known as The HOTH.</p>\n<p>The HOTH started to deliver SEO home runs one after another, and in a short period of time, we saw huge success with ranking our own clients, beating out huge, established competitor sites in extremely competitive niches.</p>\n<h3><b>The Beginning</b></h3>\n<p>After The HOTH was well established, we decided to release our first product out to the world as a<span> </span><a title=\"white label seo\" href=\"https://www.thehoth.com/\">white label seo service</a><span> </span>and let other agencies and publishers take advantage of the solution that took us so long to develop. Our agencies can take on more clients and rank them more consistently, all while doing LESS work. We know that the more successful the agencies and publishers are, the more work they will send our way.</p>\n<p>The HOTH grew quickly and caught on with agencies around the world. We established a white<span> </span><a title=\"Reseller SEO\" href=\"https://www.thehoth.com/tour/resellers/\">label seo reseller program</a><span> </span>to help agencies and consultants resell our services as well as give bulk discounts on<span> </span><a title=\"seo packages\" href=\"https://www.thehoth.com/products/\">our products</a> to our larger customers.</p>\n<h3><b>Growth &amp; Expansion</b></h3>\n<p>We realized that agencies have more needs than just general link building – so we started expanding our services.</p>\n<p>In 2013, we added HOTH Local, our first ever<span> </span><a href=\"https://www.thehoth.com/local/\">local seo service</a>. HOTH Local focuses on a very smart, well thought out process for procuring diverse types of citations to help customers rank in local searches. We also released our<span> </span><a title=\"local citation cleanup service\" href=\"https://www.thehoth.com/local/citation-cleanup-service/\">citation cleanup service</a><span> </span>to help with inconsistent or incorrect citations.</p>\n<p>In 2015 we expanded the product lineup to become a full suite of products, offering<span> </span><a href=\"https://www.thehoth.com/guestpost/\">white hat guest posts</a>,<span> </span><a href=\"https://www.thehoth.com/press/\">press releases</a>, and more.</p>\n<p>In 2016 we grew bigger than ever – our conference circut grew to SMX, Pubcon, BrightonSEO, and AdTech. We launched our<span> </span><a href=\"https://www.thehoth.com/blogger/\">blog content service</a><span> </span>called HOTH Blogger AND re-launched it with an in-dashboard experience! We also added our first<span> </span><a href=\"https://www.thehoth.com/onpage/\">OnPage SEO service</a>.</p>\n<p>In 2017 we took our growth to another level by launching our managed SEO product, HOTH X, which quickly became our top selling product.</p>\n<p>Our growth landed us on the<span> </span><a href=\"https://www.inc.com/profile/the-hoth\">Inc. 5000 list</a><span> </span>as one of the fastest growing companies in the country. With such growth, we figured it was time for a move so we packed up our 6th floor office and moved to the penthouse suite in our building,<span> </span><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kDU0kWZInoo\">take a look</a>! We also continued our conference circuit with our CMO, Clayton Johnson,<span> </span><a href=\"https://www.thehoth.com/blog/brand-reputation-hacking/\">speaking at SEJ Summit</a><span> </span>in Chicago.</p>\n<p>2018 was a great year with several new additions to The HOTH including<span> </span><a href=\"https://web.archive.org/web/20190113050641/http://www.hothcon.com:80/store-front\">HOTHCON</a>, our SEO and content marketing conference, and<span> </span><a href=\"https://www.thehoth.com/hoth-video/\">HOTH Video</a>, our newest product that turns blog articles into videos.</p>\n<p>We were fortunate enough to receive recognition as a nominee of Tampa Bay Business Journal’s<span> </span><a href=\"https://www.bizjournals.com/tampabay/news/2018/04/19/meet-the-hoth-a-2018-best-places-to-work-honoree.html\">Best Places to Work Award</a><span> </span>and<span> </span><a href=\"https://www.bizjournals.com/tampabay/news/2018/02/14/light-bright-airy-and-modern-see-tampa-bays.html\">Best Office Space Award</a>. While a lot of hard work went into accomplishing these feats, we made sure to kick back and relax the second weekend in February on our company cruise to Mexico!</p>\n<h3><b>Today &amp; Beyond</b></h3>\n<p>Our goal is to be the most reliable source for SEO tools &amp; services in the world.</p>\n<p>We continue to develop the HOTH with constant upgrades and testing to ensure the best possible results. You can find us at national and international tradeshows like SMX, BrightonSEO, Pubcon, AdTech, Affiliate Summit, and more.</p>\n<p>You can head over to our company blog to see what we’re currently up to at<span> </span><a href=\"https://www.thehoth.com/blog/\">The HOTH Company SEO Blog</a>.</p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_url=\"https://www.thehoth.com/case-studies/\" url_new_window=\"on\" button_text=\"Get A Free HOTH Account!\" button_alignment=\"center\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" custom_margin=\"50px||0px||false|false\" locked=\"off\"][/et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=\"1_3,1_3,1_3\" module_class=\"newletter-sec9 newletter-sec9-about\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#e22d1b\" width=\"100%\" max_width=\"886px\" custom_padding=\"20px|0px|20px|0px|true|true\" locked=\"off\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\" module_class=\"newletter-sec9-col newletter-sec9-col1\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_text module_class=\"newletter-sec9-col-text\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"]<h4>Talk SEO Strategy with an Expert</h4>\nSign up now and receive a free consultation from an SEO expert at The HOTH.[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\" module_class=\"newletter-sec9-col newletter-sec9-col2\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_image src=\"https://wp.localserverweb.com/thehoth/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/img__strategy-svg.png\" title_text=\"img__strategy-svg\" module_class=\"newletter-sec9-col-img\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\" module_clas