dule_class=\"simple-text1\" hover_enabled=\"0\"]<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Google Ads (Adwords) PPC Management Services</strong></h1>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Start Advertising On The World’s Largest Ad Platform</p>\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" module_class=\"good-news-sec2\" hover_enabled=\"0\" border_width_all=\"2px\" border_color_all=\"#e22d1b\" background_color=\"#f8f6f6\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" module_class=\"good-news-sec2-text\" custom_padding=\"30px|20px|30px|20px|false|false\" max_width=\"730px\" module_alignment=\"center\" hover_enabled=\"0\"]<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Good news, HOTH PPC is on sale this month!</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Save 50% on your first month when you sign up for a 3-month contract.<br /> To get in on this deal, simply book a call with us by clicking below!</p>\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_text=\"Book A Call\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" button_alignment=\"center\" hover_enabled=\"0\" button_url=\"https://www.thehoth.com/ppc-strategy-session/\" url_new_window=\"on\"][/et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" hover_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_divider _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#f2f2f2\" height=\"1px\" hover_enabled=\"0\" border_color_all=\"#cccccc\" border_width_all_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" color=\"#efefef\"][/et_pb_divider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" column_structure=\"1_2,1_2\" module_class=\"home-column-sec3\" hover_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" module_class=\"column-sec3-text\" hover_enabled=\"0\"]<h2>PPC Services That Grow Businesses</h2>\n<p>With HOTH PPC, we get you set up to advertise on Google and generate high quality leads into your business.\n\nIt’s our fully managed PPC service designed to deliver you handpicked leads directly to your business.\n\nRunning paid traffic successfully takes a multi-faceted approach. At the core, paid traffic requires knowing your numbers, but also takes strategy, creativity, and a high level of knowledge of the ad platform.\n\nThrough our innovative paid advertising process, we put your campaigns on a strategic path to ROI.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_image src=\"https://wp.localserverweb.com/thehoth/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/illustrations__ppc-overview.png\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" title_text=\"illustrations__ppc-overview\" align=\"center\" hover_enabled=\"0\" module_class=\"column-sec3-img\"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" hover_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_divider _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#f2f2f2\" height=\"1px\" hover_enabled=\"0\" border_color_all=\"#cccccc\" border_width_all_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" color=\"#efefef\"][/et_pb_divider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" column_structure=\"1_2,1_2\" module_class=\"home-column-sec3\" hover_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_image src=\"https://wp.localserverweb.com/thehoth/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/illustrations__ppc-analysis-e1565880682131.png\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" title_text=\"illustrations__ppc-analysis-e1565880682131\" align=\"center\" hover_enabled=\"0\" module_class=\"column-sec3-img\"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" module_class=\"column-sec3-text\" hover_enabled=\"0\"]<h2>Market Analysis & Campaign Design</h2>\n<p>Google ads is an auction, which means you’re only going up against your competitors. We use advanced market analysis and campaign design to make sure that you not only can compete, but you can also beat your competitors before your prospects even click your ad. We analyze data from existing competitors from keywords, to ads, to offers to make sure you’re ready to rock from Day 1.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" hover_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_divider _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#f2f2f2\" height=\"1px\" hover_enabled=\"0\" border_color_all=\"#cccccc\" border_width_all_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" color=\"#efefef\"][/et_pb_divider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" module_class=\"request-free-ppc-sec4\" background_color=\"#f6f6f6\" border_width_all=\"2px\" border_color_all=\"#eeeeee\" custom_padding=\"25px|25px|25px|25px|true|true\" hover_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" hover_enabled=\"0\"]<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Request A Free PPC Consultation</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Talk to an expert and get all your PPC questions answered.</p>\n<ul class=\"obox-grid obox-four-column\">\n<li class=\"obox-column\" style=\"text-align: center;\">• Improve lead quality<br /> • Outperform your competition<br /> • Reduce cost per lead</li>\n<li class=\"obox-column\" style=\"text-align: center;\">• Fully track ROI<br /> • Increase conversion volume<br /> • Improve your ROI</li>\n</ul>\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_text=\"Free PPC Consultation\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" button_alignment=\"center\" hover_enabled=\"0\" button_url=\"https://www.thehoth.com/ppc-strategy-session/\" url_new_window=\"on\"][/et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" hover_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_divider _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#f2f2f2\" height=\"1px\" hover_enabled=\"0\" border_color_all=\"#cccccc\" border_width_all_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" color=\"#efefef\"][/et_pb_divider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" module_class=\"campagin-text-sec5\" hover_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" module_class=\"campagin-text-sec5-text\" hover_enabled=\"0\"]<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Campaign Types, Expertly Managed</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Choose between 4 different ad options to get the best results for your business.\nNeed help picking? <a href=\"https://www.thehoth.com/ppc-strategy-session/\">Book a call with us</a> and we’ll walk you through them.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" column_structure=\"1_4,1_4,1_4,1_4\" module_class=\"campaign-types-column-sec5\" hover_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" module_class=\"campaign-types-column-sec5-text\" hover_enabled=\"0\"]<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Full Lead Gen</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Get high quality leads &amp; form fills on autopilot.</p>\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" module_class=\"campaign-types-column-sec5-text\" hover_enabled=\"0\"]<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Call Only</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Get customers calling you with the click of a button.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" module_class=\"campaign-types-column-sec5-text\" hover_enabled=\"0\"]<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Retargeting</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Follow your website visitors around the web.</p>\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"1_4\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" module_class=\"campaign-types-column-sec5-text\" hover_enabled=\"0\"]<h3 style=\"text-align: center;\">Google Shopping</h3>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Get your products seen to grow sales and revenue.</p>\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" hover_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_divider _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#f2f2f2\" height=\"1px\" hover_enabled=\"0\" border_color_all=\"#cccccc\" border_width_all_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" color=\"#efefef\"][/et_pb_divider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" module_class=\"advanced-optimize-sec6\" hover_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" module_class=\"advanced-optimize-sec6-text\" hover_enabled=\"0\"]<h2>Advanced Optimization Strategy</h2>\n<p>You want a predictable pipeline of customers who are actually ready to buy. Proper campaign optimization is a crucial component to accomplishing this. That’s why we use our multi-step, strategic laser target process on every single campaign to deliver maximum ROI.</p>\n<p><b>1. Campaign Design &amp; Pre-Optimization</b><br>\nWe expertly design your campaigns and use our unique pre-optimization process to launch ahead of the curve. This smart strategy saves you money right out of the gate.</p>\n<p><b>2. Search Term Optimization</b><br>\nIn our second phase of optimization, we continue to refine campaigns and ensure that we’re only advertising on qualified traffic.</p>\n<p><b>3. Traffic Sculpting</b><br>\nAs we get more data, we break out adgroups and lazer target prospects. This not only increases CTR (click through rate) but lowers CPC (cost per click).</p>\n<p><b>4. Performance Optimization</b><br>\nAfter we get enough clicks and time, we can tell what keywords prove out and what to cut. We optimize campaigns performance.</p>\n<p><b>5. Scale</b><br>\nAs we find more winning combinations, the testing never stops. We keep rotating ad copy until the new contender beats the winner, which means your ads are getting better all the time. This allows you to scale your campaigns at the highest ROI.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" hover_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_divider _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#f2f2f2\" height=\"1px\" hover_enabled=\"0\" border_color_all=\"#cccccc\" border_width_all_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" color=\"#efefef\"][/et_pb_divider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" column_structure=\"1_