fault\" module_class=\"column-sec3-text\" hover_enabled=\"0\"]<h2>Market Analysis & Campaign Design</h2>\n<p>Google ads is an auction, which means you’re only going up against your competitors. We use advanced market analysis and campaign design to make sure that you not only can compete, but you can also beat your competitors before your prospects even click your ad. We analyze data from existing competitors from keywords, to ads, to offers to make sure you’re ready to rock from Day 1.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" hover_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_divider _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#f2f2f2\" height=\"1px\" hover_enabled=\"0\" border_color_all=\"#cccccc\" border_width_all_last_edited=\"on|desktop\" color=\"#efefef\"][/et_pb_divider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" module_class=\"request-free-ppc-sec4\" background_color=\"#f6f6f6\" border_width_all=\"2px\" border_color_all=\"#eeeeee\" custom_padding=\"25px|25px|25px|25px|true|true\" hover_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" hover_enabled=\"0\"]<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Request A Free PPC Consultation</h2>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Talk to an expert and get all your PPC questions answered.</p>\n<ul class=\"obox-grid obox-four-column\">\n<li class=\"obox-column\" style=\"text-align: center;\">• Improve lead quality<br /> • Outperform your competition<br /> • Reduce cost per lead</li>\n<li class=\"obox-column\" style=\"text-align: center;\">• Fully track ROI<br /> • Increase conversion volume<br /> • Improve your ROI</li>\n</ul>\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_text=\"Free PPC Consultation\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_