olumn][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" module_class=\"question-form-sec\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#e22d1b\"][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_text module_class=\"question-form-sec-title\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"]<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Have Any Questions?</h2>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=\"3_5,2_5\" module_class=\"question-form-sec-row\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_column type=\"3_5\" module_class=\"question-form-sec-row-col\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"]<h3>Book a Call</h3>\n<p>Talk to one of our experts to come up with a strategy that works best for you and your company for free!</p>[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_url=\"#\" button_text=\"View Availability\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" custom_button=\"on\" button_text_size=\"14px\" button_text_color=\"#e22d1b\" button_bg_color=\"#ffffff\" button_border_width=\"2px\" button_border_color=\"#ffffff\" button_border_radius=\"0px\" button_use_icon=\"off\"][/et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"2_5\" module_class=\"question-form-sec-row-col\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" module_class=\"question-formbox-in\" hover_enabled=\"0\"]<p>[contact-form-7 id=\"67\" title=\"Contact form 1\"]</p>\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_row column_structure=\"1_2,1_2\" module_class=\"home-column-sec3 vertical-align-middle\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" hover_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_image src=\"https://wp.localserverweb.com/thehoth/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/satisfaction-guarantee-svg.png\" title_text=\"satisfaction-guarantee-svg\" align=\"center\" module_class=\"column-sec3-img\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" hover_enabled=\"0\" max_width=\"300px\"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" hover_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_text module_class=\"column-sec3-text\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" hover_enabled=\"0\"]<h2>100% Satisfaction Guarantee</h2>\n<p>We want you to feel confident in every purchase you make with us, which is why we are offering a 100% satisfaction guarantee. If for any reason you are not satisfied with our product, <a href=\"https://www.thehoth.com/ticket\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">contact our support</a> within 30 days of receiving your report and we’ll work with you to make it right!</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_divider color=\"#efefef\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#f2f2f2\" height=\"1px\" border_color_all=\"#cccccc\" border_width_all_tablet=\"\" border_width_all_phone=\"\" border_width_all_last_edited=\"on|desktop\"][/et_pb_divider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" module_class=\"faq-sec\" hover_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" module_class=\"faq-sec-title\" hover_enabled=\"0\"]<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">F.A.Q.</h2>\n[/et_pb_text][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" module_class=\"faq-sec-list\" max_width=\"760px\" module_alignment=\"center\" hover_enabled=\"0\"]<p><b>Do you have a downloadable overview?</b></p>\n<p>Yes! <a href=\"http://downloads.thehoth.com/hoth-ppc-overview.pdf\">Click here to download the pdf.</a></p>\n<p><b>Do you need access to my Google Ad Account?</b></p>\n<p>Yes, we do. We will just need your 10 digit account ID. Once we have your Google Acct. ID we will request access.</p>\n<p><strong>Who Is This For?</strong></p>\n<p>PPC is best suited for:</p>\n<p>1. Businesses who are already generating consistent sales<br /> If you are not getting consistent sales, you should use organic or free methods to confirm product-market fit before trying to scale with PPC.</p>\n<p>2. Businesses that can spend a minimum of $1,000 per month in Adspend<br /> In order to get enough data, you need to spend enough.</p>\n<p>3. Businesses that can commit to at least 3 months<br /> The launch phase of a campaign is the most important as we find the keywords that are converting and optimize the campaigns. Although we have no contracts, you’ll want to stick around for at least 3 months so we can hone in the campaigns.</p>\n<p><strong>What if I don’t have a Google Ad Account?</strong><br /> If you don’t have a Google Ad Account, you can set one up <a href=\"https://ads.google.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>What niches do you not accept?</strong>We do not accept niches that are against Google’s Advertising policy, found <a href=\"https://support.google.com/adspolicy/topic/1626336?hl=en&amp;ref_topic=2996750,1308156\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>. Additionally, we don’t accept advertising on PPC terms (i.e. we won’t run ads for you to get PPC clients) as it would be a conflict of interest for us.</p>\n<p><strong>How much do I need to be involved?</strong><br /> <strong>How does pricing and payments work?</strong></p>\n<p>Our tiers are designed based on total Ad Spend. You pay the actual ad spend directly to Google, and we simply charge the management fee. Please note, we are unable to offer refunds for any ad spend paid to Google. Once ad spend payments are made to Google, they are final.</p>\n<p><strong>Do you keep my credit card on file for ad spend?</strong></p>\n<p>No, this is kept on file inside your Google Ads account and you’re charged directly from Google.</p>\n<p><strong>Will I receive reports?</strong></p>\n<p>Yes, our goal is to 100% transparent with you at all times. First, you’ll get a custom dashboard that you can access 24/7 to check the performance of your campaigns. Secondly, you’ll receive weekly updates from your campaign manager.</p>\n<p><strong>Do you take care of the keyword research or do I need to do that?</strong></p>\n<p>We handle everything from the keyword, competitor, and offer research. In the initial onboarding form, we do ask what keywords and terms you want to advertise for. That will help point us in the right direction for initial research.</p>\n<p><strong>How can I calculate what my monthly Ad Spend should be?</strong></p>\n<p>In the case of a simple lead gen campaign, you can get a rough average by using the formula below:</p>\n<p>(Number of Leads Goal * Average CPC) / Landing Page Conversion Rate = Monthly Target Ad Spend</p>\n<p>Example:<br /> (20 Leads * $5 CPC) / .10 landing page conversion rate = $1000 per month<br /> Total ad spend required to hit the lead goal of 20 is $1000.You can also use our <a href=\"https://www.thehoth.com/ppc-roi-calculator/\">PPC calculator here.</a></p>\n<p><strong>Standard Metrics To Use</strong>Find your average conversion rate by industry <a href=\"https://unbounce.com/average-conversion-rates-landing-pages/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>.<br /> Find your average cost per click by industry <a href=\"https://www.codedesign.org/ppc-industry-benchmarks/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">here</a>.</p>\n<p><strong>Where do you run ads?</strong></p>\n<p>Right now our PPC managed services offer placement on the search network and display network.</p>\n<p><strong>Will I have access to the account?</strong></p>\n<p>Yes, you will have access. You will be able to pop in at any time and view what is going on.</p>\n<p><strong>Will I own the ad account?</strong></p>\n<p>Yes, you will own the ad account.</p>\n<p><strong>Is reporting white-label?</strong></p>\n<p>Our reports are fully white-labeled and have no HOTH branding.</p>\n<p><strong>Need help adding a CNAME record to your domain provider?</strong></p>\n<p>Find your domain provider below and click the link to see their step by step instructions.</p>\n<ul class=\"simple-list--dots\">\n<li><a href=\"https://www.godaddy.com/help/add-a-cname-record-19236\">Godaddy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://support.google.com/a/answer/47283?hl=en\">Google</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://support.hostgator.com/articles/how-to-change-dns-zones-mx-cname-and-a-records\">HostGator</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.namecheap.com/support/knowledgebase/article.aspx/9646/2237/how-to-create-a-cname-record-for-your-domain\">Namecheap</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://help.dreamhost.com/hc/en-us/articles/215414867-How-do-I-add-custom-DNS-records-\">Dreamhost</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.name.com/support/articles/115004895548-Adding-a-CNAME-Record\">Name</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://support.dnsimple.com/articles/manage-cname-record/\">DNSIMPLE</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.ionos.com/help/domains/configuring-cname-records-for-subdomains/configuring-a-cname-record-for-a-subdomain/\">1&amp;1</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://my.bluehost.com/hosting/help/cname#create\">Bluehost</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Can I run traffic to my website or landing page?</strong></p>\n<p>With our strategy, we run traffic directly to our custom landing pages that we build for your offer.</p>\n<p><strong>Do you do remarketing?</strong>Yes, as long as you have 100 unique visitors to your website in the last 30 days and it is connected to your Google Ad account for over 30 days. You can learn more <a href=\"https://support.google.com/google-ads/answer/2472738?hl=en\">here</a>.</p>\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_divider color=\"#efefef\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#f2f2f2\" height=\"1px\" border_color_all=\"#cccccc\" border_width_all_tablet=\"\" border_width_all_phone=\"\" border_width_all_last_edited=\"on|desktop\"][/et_pb_divider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"4_4\"][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_divider color=\"#efefef\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#f2f2f2\" height=\"1px\" border_color_all=\"#cccccc\" border_width_all_tablet=\"\" border_width_all_phone=\"\" border_width_all_last_edited=\"on|desktop\"][/et_pb_divider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"4_4\"][et_pb_image src=\"https://wp.localserverweb.com/thehoth/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/graphic__in-the-press@4x.png\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" module_class=\"bottom-clients-sec-img\" title_text=\"graphic__in-the-press@4x\" align=\"center\" hover_enabled=\"0\"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_section fb_built=\"1\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" module_class=\"start-alert-sec\" background_color=\"#ef3d2f\" hover_enabled=\"0\" custom_padding=\"2px|10px|2px|10px|true|true\"][et_p