ext module_class=\"column-sec3-text\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"]<h2>All The Bells & Whistles</h2>\n<p>With HOTH PPC, you get the best of the best when it comes to an all in one package for advertising. From account setups, conversion tracking, call tracking and more.</p>\n<p>Depending on your situation, we can run Search Campaigns, Display Campaigns, and Call-Only Campaigns to maximize your results.</p>\n<p>Our goal is to make the complicated world of Google Ads accessible to anyone, from start to finish. You’re in good hands with HOTH PPC.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_divider color=\"#efefef\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#f2f2f2\" height=\"1px\" border_color_all=\"#cccccc\" border_width_all_tablet=\"\" border_width_all_phone=\"\" border_width_all_last_edited=\"on|desktop\"][/et_pb_divider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=\"1_2,1_2\" module_class=\"home-column-sec3\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_text module_class=\"column-sec3-text\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"]<h2>Google Certified Partner</h2>\n<p>We are proud to hold the prestigious title of being a Google Partner.\nAchieving Partner status means The HOTH has demonstrated Google Ads skill and expertise. In addition, we have met Google ad spend requirements, delivered company agency & client revenue growth, and grown our client base.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_image src=\"https://wp.localserverweb.com/thehoth/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/google-partner-RGB-search-vid-disp.jpg\" title_text=\"google-partner-RGB-search-vid-disp\" align=