 connect with you regularly throughout this process so you\'re always in the know.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_text module_class=\"how-it-works-sec10-rowcol-text\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"]<h5>Step 3</h5>\n<p><b>Optimize, Scale, & Reporting</b></p>\n<p>Our unique, multi-stage optimization process ensures your campaigns are producing at optimal levels, at all times. With weekly reporting and a dedicated campaign manager, you’ll have full confidence in what’s happening with your campaigns.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_divider color=\"#efefef\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#f2f2f2\" height=\"1px\" border_color_all=\"#cccccc\" border_width_all_tablet=\"\" border_width_all_phone=\"\" border_width_all_last_edited=\"on|desktop\"][/et_pb_divider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row module_class=\"packeges-price-sec11\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_text module_class=\"packeges-price-sec11-title\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"]<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Packages &amp; Pricing</h2>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=\"1_2,1_2\" module_class=\"packeges-price-sec11-row\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" module_class=\"packeges-price-sec11-title-col\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_code module_class=\"pricing-table\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"]<table class=\"pricing2\"><!-- [et_pb_line_break_holder] --><tbody><!-- [et_pb_line_break_holder] --><tr><!-- [et_pb_line_break_holder] -