et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_divider color=\"#efefef\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" background_color=\"#f2f2f2\" height=\"1px\" border_color_all=\"#cccccc\" border_width_all_tablet=\"\" border_width_all_phone=\"\" border_width_all_last_edited=\"on|desktop\"][/et_pb_divider][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row column_structure=\"1_2,1_2\" module_class=\"home-column-sec3\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_text module_class=\"column-sec3-text\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"]<h2>PPC Services That Grow Businesses</h2>\n<p>With HOTH PPC, we get you set up to advertise on Google and generate high quality leads into your business.\n\nIt’s our fully managed PPC service designed to deliver you handpicked leads directly to your business.\n\nRunning paid traffic successfully takes a multi-faceted approach. At the core, paid traffic requires knowing your numbers, but also takes strategy, creativity, and a high level of knowledge of the ad platform.\n\nThrough our innovative paid advertising process, we put your campaigns on a strategic path to ROI.</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_2\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_image src=\"https://wp.localserverweb.com/thehoth/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/illustrations__ppc-overview.png\" title_text=\"illustrations__ppc-overview\" align=\"center\" module_class=\"column-sec3-img\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][/et_pb_image][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_column type=\"4_4\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\"][et_pb_divider color=\"#efefef\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _