ed us to serve and help over 200,000 businesses. In our 10 years in the SEO game, we’ve managed to make it on the Inc. 5000 list 3 years in a row, and land <a href=\"#awards\">several other cool awards</a>. </p>\n\nCheck out how we’ve HOTH’d our customers in the past:\n\nWe put our names and faces on The HOTH, made support a PRIORITY and gave out guarantees. We developed an entire suite of products to fit your needs.[/et_pb_text][et_pb_button button_url=\"https://www.thehoth.com/case-studies/\" url_new_window=\"on\" button_text=\"SEO & PPC Case Studies\" button_alignment=\"left\" _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" hover_enabled=\"0\" locked=\"off\"][/et_pb_button][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"1_2\"][et_pb_video _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=n2toj_yAx2Q&feature=youtu.be\" module_class=\"abou-column-video\" hover_enabled=\"0\"][/et_pb_video][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][et_pb_row _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" module_class=\"abou-newsletter-sec-3\" hover_enabled=\"0\" column_structure=\"3_5,2_5\" border_width_all=\"7px\" border_color_all=\"#d3d3d3\" max_width=\"700px\" custom_margin=\"80px||50px||false|false\" custom_padding=\"||||false\"][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"3_5\" module_class=\"abou-newsletter-sec-3-col abou-newsletter-sec-3-col1\" hover_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_text _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" module_class=\"abou-newsletter-sec-3-col-text\" hover_enabled=\"0\"]<h3>Want to learn more about The HOTH?</h3>\n<p>Sign up for our newsletter to learn more about who we are and all the cool stuff we do!</p>[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column _builder_version=\"4.5.1\" _module_preset=\"default\" type=\"2_5\" module_class=\"abou-newsletter-sec-3-col abou-newsletter-sec-3-col2\" hover_enabled=\"0\"][et_pb_image src=\"https://wp.localserve